{"fields":[{"t":"B","v":"true","n":"HasPrompt"},{"t":"B","v":"true","n":"HasRevealJoke4"},{"t":"B","v":"true","n":"HasRevealJoke5"},{"t":"B","v":"true","n":"HasRevealPrompt0"},{"t":"B","v":"true","n":"HasRevealJoke2"},{"t":"B","v":"true","n":"HasRevealPrompt1"},{"t":"B","v":"true","n":"HasRevealJoke3"},{"t":"B","v":"true","n":"HasRevealPrompt2"},{"t":"B","v":"true","n":"HasRevealJoke0"},{"t":"B","v":"true","n":"HasRevealJoke1"},{"t":"B","v":"false","n":"HasRevealPrompt7"},{"t":"B","v":"false","n":"HasRevealPrompt8"},{"t":"B","v":"false","n":"HasRevealPrompt3"},{"t":"B","v":"true","n":"HasRevealPrompt4"},{"t":"B","v":"true","n":"HasRevealPrompt5"},{"s":"Was für ein Moment, das herauszufinden, was?","t":"A","v":"804428_1","n":"RevealJoke5"},{"s":"Eigentlich soll ich neutral bleiben, aber du bist ein widerlicher Mensch.","t":"A","v":"804427_1","n":"RevealJoke4"},{"s":"Sprich bitte in deiner Alien-Muttersprache.","t":"A","v":"807274_1","n":"RevealPrompt2"},{"s":"Wie heißen deine geheimen Kinder?","t":"A","v":"807273_1","n":"RevealPrompt1"},{"s":"Wer hat gerade wahrscheinlich am meisten Bargeld dabei?","t":"A","v":"807276_1","n":"RevealPrompt4"},{"s":"","t":"A","n":"RevealPrompt3"},{"s":"Deine Augen haben dich verraten.","t":"A","v":"804426_1","n":"RevealJoke3"},{"s":"Ich weiß, du hast viele Mäuler zu stopfen. Schon mal Knabberpunkte probiert?","t":"A","v":"804425_1","n":"RevealJoke2"},{"s":"Was war das Ekligste, das du je gegessen hast?","t":"A","v":"807277_1","n":"RevealPrompt5"},{"s":"Ich gebe den Buchhaltern die Schuld.","t":"A","v":"804424_1","n":"RevealJoke1"},{"s":"Was würdest du lieber tun, statt mit Leuten, die du offensichtlich hasst, ein Partyspiel zu spielen?","t":"A","n":"RevealPrompt8"},{"s":"Wenn es nur eine ist, ist es halb so wild.","t":"A","v":"804423_1","n":"RevealJoke0"},{"s":"Wie lautet dein geheimes Codewort, mit dem du anderen Aliens zeigst, dass du auch eins bist?","t":"A","n":"RevealPrompt7"},{"s":"Wo würdest du eine Leiche verstecken?","t":"A","v":"807272_1","n":"RevealPrompt0"},{"s":"Was sind eure wahrscheinlichsten dunklen Geheimnisse?","t":"A","v":"804416_1","n":"Prompt"}]}